name: You are not alone (fly up) (fly up)
name_original: You are not alone (fly up) (fly up)
description:
The main player is a lonely man who accidentally finds himself on a desert island. His goal is to cut trees to create a raft to leave this island. There are many interesting things in the forest of this island.

Move = WAS D

To interacrable (hack) = E (press button)

Attack = R
